ns2:Operation.description: Enables a client system to create a safety report record in the Safety Reporting System with all fields required for safety report creation.
ns2:Operation.name: initiateSafetyReport

ns2:Operation.description: Provides the capability to associate adverse events to a safety report.
ns2:Operation.name: associateAdverseEventsToSafetyReport

ns2:Operation.description: Provides the capability to dissociate an adverse event from a safety report.
ns2:Operation.name: dissociateAdverseEventsFromSafetyReport

ns2:Operation.description: Provides the capability to update the adverse event information in the safety report.
ns2:Operation.name: updateAdverseEventInformationInSafetyReport

ns2:Operation.description: Provides the capability to associate a study to a safety report.

ns2:Operation.description: Provides the capability to associate additional information to a safety report.
